{"tid":788831,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"坐地鐵撞到女舊同學","createTime":"2018-08-21T19:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T13:15:59.000Z","uid":112551,"like":3,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"57c70fc7a1997ba7333ca11edf790b7ac8ffd4db","tid":788831,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T19:41:04.000Z","msg":"尋日坐地鐵撞到女舊同學，佢起另一架車廂見到我就行過來。<br />\n咁我同佢Say個Hi，問佢近況。我見佢同個男朋友（Facebook寫）一齊，不過個時只係得佢行過來同我打招呼。<br />\n咁我問個女同學「個男仔係咪妳既男友呢？」，之後佢竟然話只係普通朋友，仲私底下約我出街食飯。<br />\n<br />\n究竟咩事？唔通就散想搵我做佢男友？佢男友係IVE讀，成個MK仔咁款，又無咩錢。但我就唔同，唔通佢玩厭咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0002a3c98a134402fd582c45ee5887390f0f4d","tid":788831,"uid":118146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T19:44:16.000Z","msg":"咪ff咁多啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d39401d796f0ff3e700357cd55d7c9d257b7998","tid":788831,"uid":88963,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T19:45:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">夜喇 訓啦</span>"},{"pid":"fb23bcc4ff08e677d0fe2de757f476e5278eae61","tid":788831,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T19:45:59.000Z","msg":"夠鐘收皮啦"},{"pid":"2a07074e8ec26e2f1c88f861b38dc82b0600264e","tid":788831,"uid":135928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T20:05:59.000Z","msg":"普通朋友食餐飯咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主你想太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760a813decf77df5703095bfdbe0b22e79e188c2","tid":788831,"uid":142462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T20:07:16.000Z","msg":"毒撚真可怕"},{"pid":"3bd62232bc7b733ac9ed69a30b4df2e1262f1b32","tid":788831,"uid":104268,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T21:12:22.000Z","msg":"You are that MK son<